{"tid":2144069,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"委任選舉主任 一定要係政府AO？","createTime":"2020-08-07T12:58:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T13:43:04.000Z","uid":301327,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0829a2c6595f5581b13a79e64a012c0ea0f3e412","tid":2144069,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T12:58:34.000Z","msg":"有冇其他法政巴絲打意見？ 司法覆核勝算有幾大？<br />\n<br />\n【法政奄列】DQ「DQ主任」？！（劉偉聰）<br />\nDQ主任雖然專責DQ，但其正名不叫DQ，叫RO（Returning Officer 選舉主任）！<br />\n. . .<br />\n<br />\n那麼選舉管理委員會為何委任政務官出任RO？由公務員出任RO有肉眼可見的利益衝突，事關有太多立法會準候選人跟行政機關過不去，看不過眼才出選以服務人民，但把關者RO卻是官府中人，怎能令人信服他們可無畏無懼無偏無私來審核一眾反政府的參選人參選資格？硬要政務官公務員出任「不得視為政府的受僱人」的選舉管理委員會所委任的RO，先天已是不合理不可能（inherently unreasonable and impossible)，能不叫人嘩然！. . .<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200807/6YVI6AZDGMNMIIC6SEWTJFYAXQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200807%2F6YVI6AZDGMNMIIC6SEWTJFYAXQ%2F&d=1Tw5YvH57m5vrKXwbFhC6IpBSCas1SUWCM4mOsPk5ns%3D&h=1f97f963\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200807%2F6YVI6AZDGMNMIIC6SEWTJFYAXQ%2F&h=973b57c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200807/6YVI6AZDGMNMIIC6SEWTJFYAXQ/</a>"},{"pid":"f547cf9ce9076c90f9ac953d9ec1bfb53b9c7948","tid":2144069,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T12:59:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"190fbfedbe3b65f11d42dafa2578e3abe2d963f2","tid":2144069,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T13:00:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0640786d1e5853b0d505aa5c7fd99fd3b3a21d03","tid":2144069,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T13:01:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bb31cf1d527571ff7a14735b8d120adca26a69ab","tid":2144069,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T13:01:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d5c5cb73486a1af263a5997dee5fce3eb9360c0"